- Han VX companion paper in Molecular Psychiatry (PMID 40885847): reduced TNF/IL-6 TLR responses in PANS. Same group/data as Neurology N&NI paper (PMID 40953324). GEO data STILL NOT deposited — GSE278694 confirmed UNRELATED (PDAC pancreatic cancer dataset). No valid accession exists.
- New tools: MMPred (PMID 39722794, MHC-II mimicry prediction), ImmunoStruct (Nat Mach Intell 2026, pMHC immunogenicity), TITANiAN (bioRxiv May 2025, T-cell epitope prediction). All relevant to GAS mimicry + HLA projects.
